        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>mild hake curry</strong> over the <strong>sultana rice </strong>and enjoy!</p><p><strong><span class=\"text-danger\">Loved this recipe? Us too! That’s why it’s one of our Everyday Favourites, available every week.</span></strong></p>",
